    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Medical)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 4</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 16 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 4 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 16</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> H, Mas</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>If the subject is affected by a paralysis effect that did not stem from a mind-affecting ability or technique, it can save to end it, gaining a +4 bonus to the check. The DC is the same as the one from the original effect that caused the @Condition[paralyzed;remove]{paralysis}.</p>\n\n\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> The first, third and fifth step increase the bonus granted by +1 each. The fifth step allows you to use this technique on yourself once per day, even while paralyzed.</p>\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
